sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as fms-guardrails-orchestrator<br/>(Client)
    participant Server as NeMo Guardrails Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant InputRails as Input Rails Engine<br/>(In-process)
    participant Embedding as Embedding Model<br/>(Local - FastEmbed/spaCy)
    participant LLM as Backend LLM<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails Engine<br/>(In-process)

    Note over Orchestrator,OutputRails: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Guardrails

    Orchestrator->>Server: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP<br/>No Auth (internal)
    activate Server

    Server->>InputRails: Evaluate input rails<br/>(content safety, jailbreak, topic)
    activate InputRails
    InputRails->>Embedding: Generate embeddings<br/>(in-process)
    Embedding-->>InputRails: Embedding vectors
    InputRails-->>Server: Input rail result<br/>(pass/block)
    deactivate InputRails

    alt Input Rails PASS
        Server->>LLM: Forward prompt<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>API Key / Bearer Token
        activate LLM
        LLM-->>Server: LLM response
        deactivate LLM

        Server->>OutputRails: Evaluate output rails<br/>(hallucination, fact-check, content safety)
        activate OutputRails
        OutputRails-->>Server: Output rail result<br/>(pass/modify/block)
        deactivate OutputRails

        alt Output Rails PASS
            Server-->>Orchestrator: Chat completion response<br/>HTTP 200
        else Output Rails BLOCK
            Server-->>Orchestrator: Blocked response<br/>HTTP 200 (with guardrail message)
        end
    else Input Rails BLOCK
        Server-->>Orchestrator: Blocked response<br/>HTTP 200 (with guardrail message)
    end
    deactivate Server

    Note over Orchestrator,OutputRails: Flow 2: Guardrail Check (No LLM Generation)

    Orchestrator->>Server: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP<br/>No Auth (internal)
    activate Server
    Server->>InputRails: Evaluate rails<br/>(input/output/tool rails)
    activate InputRails
    InputRails->>Embedding: Generate embeddings<br/>(in-process)
    Embedding-->>InputRails: Embedding vectors
    InputRails-->>Server: Rail evaluation result
    deactivate InputRails
    Server-->>Orchestrator: Check result<br/>HTTP 200
    deactivate Server
